channel.description:
Hello, I am hoping to make a definitive list of all of the client configurations which can be changed (Like buttons going red, prayers lighting up, tracks being changed from red to green, quests being made from red to green).

Here are some I found on Rune-Pooper

<blockquote>IDS for changing frame 36, - By gander
171 : chat effects on/off
170 : MouseButtons one/two
287 : SPLIT PRIVATE CHAT ON/OFF
427 : ACCEPT AID YES/NO
166 : BRIGHTNESS 
--- prayers ---
83: THICK SKIN
84 BURST OF STRENGTH
85: CLARITY OF THOUGHT
86: ROCK SKIN
87: SUPERHUMAN STRENGTH
88: IMPROVED REFLEXES
89 RAPID RESTORE
90: RAPID HEAL
91: PROTECT ITEMS
92 STEAL SKIN
93: ULTIMATE STRENGTH
94: INCREDABLE REFLEXES
95: PROTECT FROM MAGIC
96: PROTECT FROM RANGE
97: PROTECT FROM MELE
98: RETRIBUTION
99: RENDEMPTION
100: SMITE
172: ON OFF INFORMATION SCREEN
-- player controls
WALK/RUN : 173</blockquote>

And I have also done these myself:

<blockquote>setClientConfig(18,1); //Switches between man and auto on music tab 1 = auto 0 = man
setClientConfig(19,0);//Switches loop on and off in music tab on = 1
setClientConfig(20, 0); //Activates Adventure (Song)
setClientConfig(25,0); //Activates Shining (Song)
setClientConfig(43,0); //Weapon Menu (AttackType) First option = 0 etc</blockquote>

